==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Opah
<hw>O"pah</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
large oceanic fish (<spn>Lampris guttatus</spn>), inhabiting the
Atlantic Ocean. It is remarkable for its brilliant colors, which are
red, green, and blue, with tints of purple and gold, covered with round
silvery spots. Called also <altname>king of the
herrings</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Opake</ent>⟦br⟧
